		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64246900" name="comment_link_64246900" href="//politics.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23229964&amp;cid=64246900" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64246900)" >Why doesn't this apply to corporations?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64246900" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64246900); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
