	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64247448"><p>The <i>real</i> danger posed by AI is its misuse by people who don't understand the fundamental limitations of the systems that they're using.  That's not a problem with the technology, that's a problem with people.</p><p><div class="quote"><p>think of a virus designed by an AI</p></div><p>It will necessarily be derivative and thus pose little to no actual threat.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64247448">

